{"tid":1304414,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"反對 ‘黑警治港’ 可唔可以做我地最新既主題","createTime":"2019-07-10T15:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T15:16:25.000Z","uid":81805,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7fbacff50d8a7def6b03ea1c222c0500518a1b00","tid":1304414,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:09:30.000Z","msg":"唔該大家應清楚最重要嘅係乜嘢！條例撤回都可以再重啟！<br />\n<br />\n依家香港最重要嘅問題之一係黑警治港，黑警權力過大，無人監管，令到政府硬推嘅條例好容易通過，邊個上街反對就打鳩佢！<br />\n<br />\n香港人依家最大既訴求係 <br />\n<br />\n1. 追究黑警濫權，行為不當<br />\n2. 成立獨立調查小組調查黑警<br />\n3. 釋放被捕人士，並承諾不追究<br />\n4. 削弱黑警權力，同埋成立獨立機構監察黑警<br />\n5. 立即啟動雙普選"},{"pid":"e5a0517b3a5f6f3453bb997bde4061d0c4efb8c2","tid":1304414,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:09:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1678028268d491695fea337294018ebb77beee4","tid":1304414,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"無人認同？"},{"pid":"3f7d6230a84acc146ebd985bbea38df4990654e1","tid":1304414,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d47bb5d11d5678dbb1d5c461c8626b34602912f","tid":1304414,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfce24c790b8da8ec0a9b99ecb96cef73afa4a3d","tid":1304414,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f050eee59d4fd0baf0eb359c3ef0a8a1ba00bf3","tid":1304414,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275bd03dd67827194aca1549fae51b740ebb7ffc","tid":1304414,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit